              </zone>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='56437' id='13' type-v2='text' w='97538' x='1231' y='42295'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'><![CDATA[For urban residents (red), there is a positive relationship between sleep hours and sleep quality/day energy (0.10495). The R² value (0.01635) is low, but the p-value (< 0.0001) shows the relationship is statistically significant. The urban line shows a slight upward trend, indicating that increased sleep hours improve sleep quality and daytime energy.]]></run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>For rural residents (green), a positive relationship is also observed (0.0777039), though slightly weaker than urban. The R² value (0.0083808) remains low, and the p-value (0.02493) indicates the relationship is statistically significant. The rural line also trends upward, showing improvement in sleep quality and energy with more sleep.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Overall:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Increasing sleep hours improves sleep quality/day energy for both groups, with a slightly stronger effect in urban residents.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
