              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='55899' id='11' type-v2='text' w='97538' x='1231' y='42833'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'><![CDATA[For urban residents (red), there is a negative relationship between phone use before sleep and sleep quality/day energy (-0.1547). The R² value (0.01837) is low, but the p-value (< 0.0001) indicates that the relationship is statistically significant. The urban line slopes slightly downward, showing that increased screen use reduces sleep quality and energy.]]></run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'><![CDATA[For rural residents (green), the negative relationship is stronger (-0.32768), showing a greater decline in sleep quality/day energy with increased phone use. The R² value (0.0799119) is still relatively low but higher than urban, and the p-value (< 0.0001) confirms that the relationship is statistically significant. The rural line shows a steeper downward trend, indicating a stronger negative impact.]]></run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Overall:</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Screen use before sleep negatively affects both groups, with a stronger impact observed among rural residents.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
