                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Although awareness of healthy sleep habits is already high among respondents such as reducing screen time, maintaining a consistent sleep schedule, and creating a stress-free environment, there is still a gap between knowledge and actual behavior. The strong willingness among participants to use a sleep-support mobile application further suggests an opportunity to support better sleep practices through digital tools and practical interventions.</run>
