                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='84922' id='10' type-v2='text' w='97538' x='1231' y='1268'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='14'>Urban-Rural lifestyle differences in Bhutan </run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>I am Sonam Peldon, Gedu College of Business Studies intern and data practitioner at Data Scientists Pvt. Ltd., exploring how lifestyle habits affect health and wellbeing. I created this project to examine how daily routines such as sleep, work, and screen use differ between urban and rural residents in Bhutan and how these differences influence sleep quality and daytime energy. Using these insights, Iaim to develop evidence-based tools, like a website and mobile app, to help individuals and communities improve their daily habits and overall wellbeing</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Key Areas Covered:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>1. Evidence of Lifestyle Impacts on Sleep and Wellbeing </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>2. Local Context </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>3. Purpose of the Study </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>4. Study Overview and Findings</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Æ </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>5. Recommendations for Improving Sleep Health </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>6. Key Takeaways</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
