    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Purpose'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='860' maxwidth='650' minheight='560' minwidth='420' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='84564' id='3' type-v2='text' w='97538' x='1231' y='1268'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Study Purpose:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Conducted an online survey during internship to understand lifestyle habits, sleep routines, screen use, and work patterns among urban and rural residents in Bhutan.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Sample Size:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> 366 respondents participated, providing insights into everyday behaviors.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Findings are structured into key areas:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>1. Respondent Distribution:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Context and characteristics of the sample.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>2. Core Insights:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Differences between urban and rural populations in average work hours, screen use before bedtime, and sleep duration.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>3. Correlation Insights:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> How work hours, screen time, and sleep duration relate to sleep quality and daytime energy levels.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>4. Habits Affecting Sleep Quality:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Behaviors that improve or disrupt sleep.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>5. Preferences for Sleep Support Tools:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Features respondents would like in apps or digital tools.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>6. Future Interest in Sleep Tools:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Willingness to use digital support for better sleep.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>7. Key Takeaways:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Main patterns and trends identified from the survey.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone h='12900' id='5' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='97538' x='1231' y='85832' />
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
        <devicelayout auto-generated='true' name='Phone'>
          <size maxheight='700' minheight='700' sizing-mode='vscroll' />
          <zones>
            <zone h='100000' id='13' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
              <zone h='84000' id='12' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='84000' x='8000' y='8000'>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='84564' id='3' type-v2='text' w='97538' x='1231' y='1268'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Study Purpose:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Conducted an online survey during internship to understand lifestyle habits, sleep routines, screen use, and work patterns among urban and rural residents in Bhutan.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Sample Size:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> 366 respondents participated, providing insights into everyday behaviors.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Findings are structured into key areas:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>1. Respondent Distribution:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Context and characteristics of the sample.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>2. Core Insights:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Differences between urban and rural populations in average work hours, screen use before bedtime, and sleep duration.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>3. Correlation Insights:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> How work hours, screen time, and sleep duration relate to sleep quality and daytime energy levels.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>4. Habits Affecting Sleep Quality:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Behaviors that improve or disrupt sleep.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>5. Preferences for Sleep Support Tools:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Features respondents would like in apps or digital tools.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>6. Future Interest in Sleep Tools:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Willingness to use digital support for better sleep.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>7. Key Takeaways:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> Main patterns and trends identified from the survey.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='8' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zones>
        </devicelayout>
      </devicelayouts>
      <simple-id uuid='{3B09EEB3-0959-4F51-90D2-EE4A26ED732A}' />
    </dashboard>
    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Recommendation'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='860' maxwidth='650' minheight='560' minwidth='420' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='82500' id='3' type-v2='text' w='93692' x='3692' y='2143'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>1. Reduce screen use before bedtime</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Limit screens 30–60 minutes before sleep to improve sleep quality.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>2. Keep a consistent sleep schedule</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Go to bed and wake up at the same time every day to support better rest and energy.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>3. Focus on applying good habits</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Move from knowing healthy sleep practices to actually practicing them daily with reminders and routines.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>4. Use sleep-support apps</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Apps with features like screen-time reminders, sleep tracking, and bedtime alerts can help build better habits.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>5. Adjust strategies for different groups</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Urban people may need stress and work-life balance support, while rural people may need help reducing night time screen use.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>6. Prioritize sleep as essential</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Treat sleep as a key part of health and productivity, not something optional.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>7. Include interactive website self-assessment</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Provide an online self-assessment tool where users can evaluate their sleep habits and receive personalized feedback and recommendations.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
        <devicelayout auto-generated='true' name='Phone'>
          <size maxheight='700' minheight='700' sizing-mode='vscroll' />
          <zones>
