          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Physical work is more common among rural residents, with 40 people involved compared to 60 in urban areas, showing only a small difference. In contrast, mental work is more common among urban residents, with 69 people compared to 35 in rural areas. Mixed work, which includes both physical and mental tasks, is much higher in urban areas, with 134 people, while only 40 rural residents fall into this category.</run>
